column2: SELECT ra_BCG, dec_BCG FROM MyDB.BCGs_SF_IN OPEN my_cursor WHILE (# = #) BEGIN FETCH NEXT from my_cursor into @ra_BCG, @dec_BCG IF (@@fetch_status < #) break INSERT MYDB.BCGs_SF_OUT SELECT @ra_BCG, @dec_BCG, p.ra, p.dec, p.objID, e.bpt FROM dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (@ra_BCG, @dec_BCG, #/#) n, Galaxy p JOIN emissionLinesPort AS e ON e.specObjID = p.objid WHERE n.objid = p.objid END CLOSE my_cursor DEALLOCATE my_cursor
